FBIS3-13416 "drnes049_l_94011" FBIS-NES-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Rabin Orders Detention of Golan Settler TA1303202994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 2000 GMT 13 Mar 94 TA1303202994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Mikha'el Ben-Horin, from the Golan Heights settlement of Nov, was arrested this evening after Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin signed a three-month administrative detention order against him. Ben-Horin calls himself the president of the State of Judaea and is considered one of the most radical settlers living on the Golan Heights.
